➜香港之后 荷兰和比利时也报告康复者二次感染新冠病例
http://www.sohu.com/a/414816899_162758	28202
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/0bf0750041484235ac11e37fab2a0791.jpeg" /></p>
<p>（报道截图）</p>
<p>海外网8月25日电 香港大学微生物学系团队24日证实，一名新冠肺炎康复者自欧洲返回香港后，新冠病毒检测结果再次呈阳性，为第二次感染新冠病毒，而非“复阳”，属全球首例。25日，有媒体曝出，荷兰和比利时也报告患者第二次感染新冠病毒的病例。</p>
<p>据香港《南华早报》25日报道，荷兰国家广播公司NOS当地时间25日援引病毒学家的话说，荷兰和比利时各有一名患者已被证实第二次感染了新冠病毒。荷兰患者是一个免疫系统较弱的老年人。病毒学家强调说，确定是否是第二次感染新冠病毒，需要对第一次和第二次感染的病毒进行病毒基因检测，以查明两种病毒是否略有不同。荷兰政府顾问库普曼斯表示，人们预计会再次感染新冠病毒。她说：“有人会再次感染新冠病毒，这并不会让我感到紧张，我们必须看看这是否是经常发生。”</p>
<p>报道指出，比利时患者目前有轻度症状，但“这不是一个好消息”，因为这表明患者在第一次感染时产生的抗体不足以防止第二次感染稍有不同的变异新冠病毒。病毒学家表示目前尚不清楚这种情况是否罕见，或者“还有更多的人在康复六个月或七个月后可能会再次感染新冠病毒”。（海外网 爱扎大）</p>
➜青海湖畔普氏原羚数量超过2700只
http://www.sohu.com/a/414817151_162758	28210
<p>新华社西宁8月25日电（记者李琳海、耿辉凰）青海湖国家级自然保护区管理局监测结果显示，目前青海湖畔普氏原羚数量超过2700只，小羊家族正在逐步壮大。</p>
<p>普氏原羚是国家一级保护动物，曾广泛分布于内蒙古、宁夏、甘肃、青海等省区，由于人类活动影响及栖息地恶化，目前青海湖环湖地区是普氏原羚的唯一栖息地。</p>
<p>青海湖国家级自然保护区管理局于2004年成立普氏原羚保护站，该站是我国唯一一个普氏原羚救助、人工驯养繁殖的保护站。</p>
<p>青海湖南岸保护站站长吴永林说，如今青海湖畔普氏原羚共有14个野外种群，主要分布在青海海南和海北两个藏族自治州的共和、刚察、海晏等县，数量从1994年的300余只增加到现在的2700余只。</p>
<p>今年7月10日到8月5日，青海湖南岸保护站内共有15只普氏原羚出生。</p>
<p>“随着保护力度不断加大，青海湖普氏原羚不断增加，保存建立了良好的物种基因库。”吴永林说。</p>
<p>青海湖地处青藏高原东北部，是我国最大的内陆咸水湖，维系着青藏高原生态安全，青海湖以丰富的生物多样性被称为“青藏高原物种基因库”。</p>
➜中国爱情故事：相知相守 互敬互信 钟爱一生
http://www.sohu.com/a/414817303_162758	28210
<p>纤云弄巧，七夕传情。爱情是古今中外，人类永恒的主题。中国古代诗人的笔下，爱是“天涯共此时”的相思，是“心有灵犀一点通”的契合，是“除却巫山不是云”的坚贞，是“执子之手、与子偕老”的温馨。我们不常把爱挂在嘴边，但将最美最真挚的情感融入在了日常点滴中，书写普通人含蓄而独特的浪漫。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/5ca3a51b00c84718a7c75e5763918999.jpeg" /></p>
<p>爱是陪伴。从青丝窈窕到迟暮耄耋，我们携手走过大半生风雨，用时光写一封最美情书。两个人从独立鲜明的个体，变成不能分隔的整体，是爱人，是朋友，也是亲人。即使会磕磕绊绊，对方总是愿意陪你在酸甜苦辣中尝尽人生百味，在平淡生活中一起看细水长流。在人生的列车上，我们相濡以沫、相扶相持，想要陪伴彼此更久一些。愿无岁月可回头，且余深情共白首。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/8d9e31362b7b4411a0b6bf7087bd78bc.jpeg" /></p>
<p>爱是无悔。此身为国，此心为你。我们看到那个年代的人对国家、事业、爱情的坚定信念，因为挚爱，所以无悔。此生唯祖国与你不可辜负，邓稼先夫妇用报效祖国的赤忱、岁月无改的深情，书写了一部宏大而温柔的中国爱情故事。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/a77cf2662fdf46928c806e9acc745534.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>爱是理解。从委屈埋怨，到支持和默默守护，对王仕花来说，爱就是理解你的思想，尊重你的信仰。唯有对祖国和爱人的深情，能抵过岛上漫长而艰苦的岁月。理解是无条件的信任，是无声的成就，是最好的陪伴，它让爱情在两人心里慢慢扎下根，开出同心的花，收获前行的勇气。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/2eefc521b753430bb0b6418dc5b13487.jpeg" /></p>
<p>爱是同行。最好的爱情不是物质上的门当户对，而是精神上的志同道合。在战疫的千万“逆行者”中，很多人既是夫妻，也是战友。一个支援前线，一个保障后方，不同的战场，一样的敌人。他们用小家短暂的分离，换来更多人长久的相守。经历过“同心奉献、赤诚比肩”的刻骨铭心，更能体会重逢后“胜却人间无数”的甜蜜。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/2df3ed045dab4d7fa91efbe40944eb9b.jpeg" /></p>
<p>爱是责任。我们怀着对未来美好生活的期许步入婚姻，我们也在责任担当中学会成长。夫妻作为家庭的组建者和中坚力量，有责任和义务敬老爱幼，树立优良家风，维护平等、和睦的家庭关系，成为孩子的表率。家和万事兴，爱是责任，也是动力。有了彼此温暖的臂弯，我们将有无尽的力量为一个个提升家庭幸福感的小梦想而奋斗，日子也会过得越来越甜。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/5d74d7e23b0d41feb55cca05d8398775.jpeg" /></p>
<p>爱是遛狗逗猫的日常，是并肩看夕阳的浪漫，是洗衣做饭的琐碎，是身边可以紧握的那只手。有些爱情没有鲜艳的玫瑰和精美的礼物，依旧浪漫甜蜜，依旧深沉动人。七夕节，祝福每一个收获爱情和正在勇敢奔赴爱情的人。（文字/苏芮漫画/六合发布丁雅芸、秦珏、王珺）</p>
➜40 years of development: Zhuhai Special Economic Zone
http://www.sohu.com/a/414817315_162758	28215
<p><img src="//p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/e4d96997a6c14e21a6c740f8655821f6.jpeg" /></p>
<p>Since the establishment of Zhuhai Special Economic Zone (SEZ) in 1980, Zhuhai has developed from a border town dominated by agriculture and fisheries to a central city in the Pearl River Delta driven by comprehensive economic and social development and an important city for the development in Greater Bay Area, with all-round development of science, education, culture and health, and outstanding achievements in education and continuous progress in health.</p>
<p>Zhuhai’s scientific and technological development has grown from scratch, while innovation capacity has been significantly enhanced. Zhuhai has basically established and improved the medical assistance system, implemented the universal medical insurance system, and realized the transition from the new rural cooperative medical care to basic medical insurance for urban and rural residents.</p>
<p><strong>Glorious 40 years of the SEZ</strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/f5ba38dd8d7141d793553cfb865b025e.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>Zhuhai’s GDP increased from RMB 209 million in 1979 to RMB 291.5 billion in 2018, ranking first in Guangdong Province, witnessing a remarkable improvement since the establishment of the SEZ. In 2018, Zhuhai’s per capita GDP is only second to Shenzhen among the nine cities in the Pearl River Delta of Greater Bay Area, which means that Zhuhai’s economic development has entered a higher level.</p>
<p>At the same time, Zhuhai Special Economic Zone has always adhered to the development concept of “lucid water and lush mountains are invaluable assets”, and has achieved fruitful results of building a “livable city”. It has laid a foundation for high-quality development, consolidating and enhancing its ecological advantages.</p>
<p><strong>Bright future with the Greater Bay area</strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200825/db10fee43a284faaa77a012ca09ec668.jpeg" /></p>
<p>Zhuhai enjoys a unique geographical position, facing Hong Kong across the sea in the east, while connecting Macao in the south. Since the Hong Kong-Zhuhai-Macao Bridge came into use in October 2018, Zhuhai has become the only city in the mainland both connected with Hong Kong and Macao by land, making its strategic position even more highlighted. Besides, Zhuhai enjoys convenient transportation. Intercity railways, expressways and water shipping channels seamlessly connect Hong Kong, Macao, Guangzhou and Shenzhen as well as other urban areas and airports, providing fast and comfortable transportation for international and domestic tourists to arrive in the city, meanwhile greatly shortening the commuting time with other cities, thus forming a diversified transportation system of “urban rail + intercity rail + expressway”.</p>
<p>Under the framework of Closer Economic Partnership Arrangement (CEPA), Guangdong Province will further expand its reform and opening up, which will demand Zhuhai to give full play to the advantages Hong Kong and Macao have as free ports, vigorously promoting the innovation of customs clearance system, science and technology, management system and development model, facilitating employment, residence and free exchanges of Hong Kong and Macao residents in Zhuhai, and vigorously enhancing the level of internationalization.</p>
